<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb562a978-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s970"><num value="970">§ 970.</num><heading> Noncontainerized cargo</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary, acting through the Commissioner, shall consider the potential for participation in C–TPAT by importers of noncontainerized cargoes that otherwise meet the requirements under this part.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb562a979-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/347/tII/s220">Pub. L. 109–347, title II, § 220</ref>, <date date="2006-10-13">Oct. 13, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1914">120 Stat. 1914</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
